    <item>
      <title>对俄制裁令邻国损失惨重，俄方不愿永远遵守制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/kazakhstan-will-not-blindly-follow-sanctions-on-russia-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦在执行针对俄罗斯的制裁方面采取了新的路线，誓言将自身经济利益放在首位，同时加深与伊朗和中国等国的贸易联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/kazakhstan-will-not-blindly-follow-sanctions-on-russia-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本政府加强对芯片供应链网络的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/japan-s-foreign-trade-law-adds-chip-gear-to-secure-supply-chains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本财政部周五表示，作为确保稳定供应链的努力的一部分，日本已决定对芯片制造设备实施对外贸易监管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/japan-s-foreign-trade-law-adds-chip-gear-to-secure-supply-chains</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 02:45:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普披露高尔夫俱乐部和度假村收入 5.13 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/trump-financial-filing-reveal-legal-debts-513-million-from-golf-clubs-resorts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普最新的财务披露显示，他从美国的度假胜地和住宅物业（包括他的多拉尔、海湖庄园和贝德明斯特俱乐部）获得了 5.13 亿美元的收入，同时还有与其法律纠纷相关的数千万美元的负债和债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/trump-financial-filing-reveal-legal-debts-513-million-from-golf-clubs-resorts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 01:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯因司法部调查被传唤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/nyc-mayor-eric-adams-subpoenaed-as-part-of-doj-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《纽约时报》报道，纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯因司法部腐败调查而收到传票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/nyc-mayor-eric-adams-subpoenaed-as-part-of-doj-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 01:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
